These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-1::.
Food: apple, cherry, eggplant, apricot
Nationality: mexican, nigerian, italian, dutch
1. Nationality:nigerian is on the left of Nationality:mexican##1
2. Food:apple == Nationality:dutch##1
3. Nationality:italian is on the right of Nationality:mexican##1
4. Food:cherry is on the left of Nationality:dutch##1
5. Food:apricot is on the left of Nationality:mexican##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| Food          | apricot | eggplant | cherry | apple   |
| Nationality   | nigerian  | mexican     | italian   | dutch |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-2::.
Hobby: traveling, card-games, writing, puzzles
Sport: surfing, cricket, badminton, skiing
1. Hobby:puzzles == Sport:cricket##1
2. Hobby:traveling is on the far right##1
3. Hobby:card-games is on the right of Hobby:puzzles##1
4. Hobby:puzzles is on the right of Sport:badminton##1
5. Sport:cricket is on the left of Sport:surfing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |      2      |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby   | writing | puzzles | card-games | traveling    |
| Sport   | badminton    | cricket      | surfing | skiing |

